sing of mr patrick we hodgson one of the longesttenured members of the companys board of directors who died monday december  mr hodgson joined the board of mt in  having joined the board of its subsidiary mt bank in  he was a member of the audit and executive committees of mt and of the examining executive and trust and investment committees of mt bank mr hodgsons dedication and service to mt bank extend back more than three decades and he helped to guide the transformation of our company from a local bank in western new york into a leading regional bank with operations across the northeast and midatlantic as a member of several of our board committees his expertise and guidance were invaluable to our company and our management team on behalf of the mt family we extend our sympathy and condolences to the hodgson family said mt bank chairman and ceo robert g wilmers about mt bank corporationmt is a financial holding company headquartered in buffalo new york mts principal banking subsidiary mt bank operates banking offices in new york maryland new jersey pennsylvania delaware connecticut virginia west virginia and the district of columbia trustrelated services are provided by mts wilmington trustaffiliated companies and by mt bank to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesmtbankcorporationacknowledgesthepassingofdirectorpatrickhodgsonhtml source mt bank corporation related links httpwwwmandtbankcom jan    et preview mt bank corporation announces fourth quarter  full year  earnings conference call dec    et preview mt bank increases prime rate my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen also from this source jul    et mt bank corporation announces second quarter results jul    et mt bank corporation announces dividend declaration on series a explore more news releases in similar topics banking  financial services obituaries you just read mt bank corporation acknowledges the passing of director patrick hodgson news provide